-lemma=\"ζάω\">ἔζησεν</span>  <span data-text=\"ἔτη\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ἔτη</span>  <span data-text=\"ιθ\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"ιθ\">ιθ</span>  <span data-text=\"μῆνας\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"μείς\">μῆνας</span>  <span data-text=\"γ\" data-n=\"55\" data-lemma=\"γ\">γ</span>  <span dir=\"ltr\">(vac.3)</span>  <span data-text=\"ἡμέρας\" data-n=\"70\" data-lemma=\"ἡμέρα\">ἡμέρας</span>  <span data-text=\"ια\" data-n=\"80\" data-lemma=\"ια\">ια</span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Valentina Mignosa</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>..<br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-text=\"παρθένος\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"παρθένος\">[..]..ΕΝ<span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">Ο͡Σ</span></span><span data-text=\"σεμνὴ\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"σεμνός\">ΣΕ[.].Η</span><br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span><span data-text=\"ἀμέμπτωος\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"ἄμεμπτος\">[.]ΜΕΜΠΤΟ[.</span><span data-text=\"ἔζησεν\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"ζάω\">..]ΗΣΕΝ</span><br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span><span data-text=\"ἔτη\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ΕΤΗ</span><span data-text=\"ιθ\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"ιθ\">ΙΘ</span><span data-text=\"μῆνας\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"μείς\">ΜΗ.[..]</span>·<span data-text=\"γ\" data-n=\"55\" data-lemma=\"γ\">Γ</span>·<br id=\"al5-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span data-text=\"ἡμέρας\" data-n=\"70\" data-lemma=\"ἡμέρα\">ΗΜΕΡΑΣ</span>·<span data-text=\"ια\" data-n=\"80\" data-lemma=\"ια\">ΙΑ</span>·</span></div><p class=\"miniapp\">l.3 reg., orig. .ΜΕΜΠΤΟ.ο</p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Vic